        public Client.Builder4 retryJitter(double jitter)
        Sets the level of randomness applied to the next retry interval. The next calculated retry interval is multiplied by (1 - jitter * Math.random()). A value of zero means no jitter, 1 means max jitter.
        Parameters:
        jitter - level of randomness applied to the retry interval
        Returns:
        this
